{"tid":621894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先可以同男朋友交到心？","createTime":"2018-04-08T16:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T16:47:14.000Z","uid":52486,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4220b9dfeef4665443a96819fbc0f7808704a7","tid":621894,"uid":52486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"同男朋友都一齊咗幾年<br />\n但平時同佢冇乜共同話題<br />\n講得最多嘅嘢就係打機<br />\n有時唔開心搵佢傾又好快轉話題<br />\n求其講2句廢話就當冇事<br />\n佢內心有啲咩諗法我從來都唔知<br />\n同佢講過但佢唔覺得呢個係一個問題<br />\n自問自己已經向佢坦露自己內心<br />\n但因為佢咁嘅態度令我慢慢收返埋自己<br />\n令到段關係中冇真正嘅交流<br />\n自己都開始好灰 係佢面前做唔到自己<br />\n可以點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2e474091d20251a0f68d7f217abcda71578d6b","tid":621894,"uid":33819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"係佢面前做自己"},{"pid":"e5cc321971f1064afe21ac940735d400f940f900","tid":621894,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"坦白d講，你係咪真係想了解佢！！！"},{"pid":"60821d2dca009f582d0827016b6f57ca47d45214","tid":621894,"uid":52486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa2e474091d20251a0f68d7f217abcda71578d6b","tid":621894,"uid":33819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"係佢面前做自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"試過 但唔work<br />\n感覺似雖然愛大家 但根本唔夾"},{"pid":"1094565729cd225531d0a43ad828ec5c9e965d7d","tid":621894,"uid":52486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5cc321971f1064afe21ac940735d400f940f900","tid":621894,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"坦白d講，你係咪真係想了解佢！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"想呀 但佢好似冇咁嘅心意"},{"pid":"8311b9e7e0b743413d5794079b941f1cbc5ce9ea","tid":621894,"uid":171119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"咁到底因咩而一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" 